<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77898a52-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s423h–3"><num value="423h–3">§ 423h–3.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated such sums, but not more than $90,000, as are necessary to acquire land pursuant to <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s423h–2">section 423h–2 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77898a53-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/87/603/s3">Pub. L. 87–603, § 3</ref>, <date date="1962-08-24">Aug. 24, 1962</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/76/403">76 Stat. 403</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
